text: Colette Francoise Hué (11 May 1932 - 31 March 2007) was a French gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2007 deaths Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics
